We have the following mailing lists:

* [http://lists.gobolinux.org/mailman/listinfo/gobolinux-users GoboLinux-Users]: users mailing list, in English
* [http://lists.gobolinux.org/mailman/listinfo/gobolinux-recipes GoboLinux-Recipes]: recipe submission and discussions takes place here now;
* [http://lists.gobolinux.org/mailman/listinfo/gobolinux-devel GoboLinux-Devel]: developers corner;
* [http://lists.gobolinux.org/mailman/listinfo/gobolinux-commits GoboLinux-Commits]: read-only list where commits to CVS are automatically posted;
* [http://lists.gobolinux.org/mailman/listinfo/gobolinux-arm GoboLinux-ARM]: general talk on the GoboLinux port for ARM platforms.
* [http://lists.gobolinux.org/mailman/listinfo/gobolinux-br GoboLinux-Br], the brazilian users mailing list, in Portuguese

Someday in the future we might have more gobolinux-* lists for other languages. That will be a happy day. :)

